original_title: ZsaZsa Zaturnnah Vs. The Amazonistas of Planet X
overview: A shy, small-town gay man discovers a strange meteorite that transforms him into ZsaZsa Zaturnnah, a flamboyant female superhuman ready to defend his town from all sorts of supernatural & extra terrestrial threats.
title: ZsaZsa Zaturnnah Vs. The Amazonistas of Planet X
